33...Rfe8 34.e6 Rxc6 35.Rxc6 
{
35.dxc6 Qa6 36.c7 g5 is good for black.
}
35...g5! 36.e7!? 
{
Despair, as knight moves lose, e.g., 36.Nh5 Rxe6! 
}
36...gxf4 37.gxf4 Qb5 
{
The fight is over, as black's queen is free at last.
}
38.Rf6 Qxd5+ 39.Kh3 Qf3+ 40.Kh2 Qxf4+ 41.Kh3 Qg4+ 42.Kh2 Qh4+ 43.Kg2 Qxf6 
