A serious error. Correct was 21.cxd5 exd5 (or 21...Nxd5 22.Nxd5 exd5 23.Qf6+ Kc7 24.Qd6+ Kd8 25.e6 winning) 22.c4! with a decisive attack. 
}
21...Ne4 22.cxd5 Ng5! 
{
I overlooked this nice resource. The threat of 22...Nf3+ gives Black a chance to organize a counterattack.
}
23.Kh1 
{
Not 23.Nxe6+ Bxe6 24.dxe6 Nf3+ 25.Kh1 Nxh4 26.Bb6+ Ke8 27.Bxa5 Rxg2 and Black wins. 
