1.e4 e6 2.d4 d5 3.Nc3 Nf6 4.Bg5 Bb4!? 5.e5 h6 6.Be3 Ne4 7.Qg4 Kf8 
{
This alternative to 7...g6 seems to be more reliable for Black, despite the unavailability of castling.
