Sicilian Defense B23
}
1.e4 c5 2.Nc3 d6 3.f4 Nc6 4.Nf3 g6 5.Bc4
{
Never before seen in such a high-level event.
}
5...Bg7 6.0-0 e6 7.d3 Nge7 8.Qe1 Nd4
{
This treatment has become quite popular.
}
