26.axb5 Qxb5 27.Rxf5 Kh8 28.Rxf6!
{
Smashing his way in.
}
28...Rxf6 29.Ng4 Rf5 30.Nh6 Rh5 31.Qf4
{
A very fine game by Short.
}
