}
14.Kb1 Ne5 15.Qh5 Qd8!? 
{
15...Qe7 is the more popular alternative, however by playing rare line in a sub-variation I may surprise my opponent. Afterwards Rizzitano told me that he had several games with this position I didn't even know!
